{
  "stem": "27285.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, there was no condition, as yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were probably in one of those-- I don't know how you call this in English, it's like a cell, it's very-- were soldiers used to live.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was actually the garrison--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not the barracks, it's-- yeah-- and that was-- actually, the whole of Terezin is a garrison.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they would squeeze in as much, as many people as possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was possible, I guess.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Clothing, we had our own, what we bought.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the food was rationed, but it was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, as I told you, we already were quite hungry in the orphanage, so it was nothing new.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, I didn't suffer so much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, I even earned my first food, I mean, like I told you-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, by singing, [LAUGHS] by being chosen to sing there in a few choirs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I earned my margarine and sugar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was my first professional entrance into the world of music, and earning my stay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, no, we were-- it was still a very chaotic-- the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, yes, we were-- then when we were already in the children's home, we went together to work, and together, after work, we learned together, or two of the children took the food, so we had it together.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was somehow-- this organization was also-- finally came a lady-- whom was-- so the children, maybe, I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But about-- so the children are the same age, more or less.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one grown up person, who was maybe 25, but for us, of course, very grown up already, was responsible for the children, and for the organization in that home-- cleaningness--",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
